Class Student

java.lang.Object
Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Instate, International, Outstate
public abstract class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
The superclass of all Student subclasses Provides common functions compareTo and toString and defines abstract function tuitionDue
Author:
Jared Montalbo, Noah Turbin
